Title: Fun with htop

## Advanced htop Features on Popular Unix Platforms

- customize display `C`
- search `/` or filter `\` lightweight process (LWP, aka pthread) list
- per-LWP commands
	- system trace `s`
	- list of open file descriptors `l`
	- environment variables `e`

